snippet.title: Maths trick for fast addition - add faster than a calculator!
snippet.description:
Being able to add two numbers quickly is an important maths skill.
This lesson shows how to add quickly in your head, from left to right (the way you would say the answer), through carrying numbers forward.
Mental computation - practice it - especially addition, as this is the most common use of maths used in society. To support free math by tecmath onPatreon (thankyou): https://www.patreon.com/tecmath To donate to the tecmath channel:  https://paypal.me/tecmath?locale.x=en_AU
